'''''Polyhedron'' 93''' was a roleplaying magazine published in [[April]] [[1994]]. It contained an article, "[[Crystal Web Space Station: A Setting for the Star Wars: New Republic Campaign]]," for [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]. The article was written by [[Bill Slavicsek]] and [[Michele Carter]]. Like all supplements printed in ''[[Polyhedron]]'' prior to [[2002]], the article is considered ambiguously [[canon]].

